snippet.title: Windjammers 2 - Biaggi & Raposa (Gamescom 2019)
snippet.description:
Windjammers 2 will jam on Google Stadia, Nintendo Switch and other PC platforms! 

Making their grand entrance today are two brand new characters, Loris Biaggi and Jao Raposa. Biaggi is a freshly minted legend on the windjamming court, touting some seriously impressive blocking and shooting skills, Biaggi has been a lifelong athletic legend that will impress even the most die hard jammers. Jao spent his childhood in Brazil watching the original Windjammers’ Steve Miller own his opponents on the jammin’ court, and his special moves show just how much he admires his idol. Both are absolute forces of nature on the windjamming court, so be prepared to harness their ultimate disc throwing prowesses. 

Featuring enhanced online multiplayer modes and a rad solo mode, Windjammers 2 will also make your head spin with its all new-jumps, smashes and slapshots to bring the best windjammin’ experience on the court. 

More information regarding Windjammers 2 on Google Stadia (specs, price and launch date) will be announced soon. For complete information on Windjammers 2, make sure to follow our offical accouns: 
Official Twitter Page: http://www.twitter.com/windjammers
Official Facebook Page: http://www.twitter.com/windjammers
Dotemu Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/Dotemu
